# ===========================================
# Development / planning notes — PRIVATE, not for the repo
# -------------------------------------------------------
# Personal notes you write while building. These patterns are intentionally
# specific so they do NOT hide the real, user-facing docs:
#   WORKFLOWS.md, CREATING_WORKFLOWS.md, content-requirements.md,
#   *.template.md, SKILL.md, README.md  → all stay tracked.
#
# Conventions you can use to keep a file private:
#   • prefix the name with an underscore   → _my-notes.md
#   • use a private suffix                 → design.local.md, plan.draft.md
#   • drop it in a _dev/ or notes/ folder
# ===========================================
_*.md
*.local.md
*.private.md
*.draft.md
*.wip.md
*.notes.md
*.scratch.md

# Common dev-doc filenames (any directory)
PLAN.md
PLANNING.md
IMPLEMENTATION.md
IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md
IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md
DEV_NOTES.md
DEV-NOTES.md
DEVLOG.md
SCRATCH.md
SCRATCHPAD.md
DRAFT.md
TODO.local.md

